<plot>Rahim, the son of Arabic immigrants in Switzerland, is torn between the western world he grew up in and the roots of his native culture. Although he is fully integrated in Switzerland, he still feels treated with skepticism and prejudice. Recruited to commit a terrorist attack, Rahim is now preparing to fulfill his mission ... and realizes that he hasn't come to terms with his fate just yet.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?087382</url></doc>
